OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSoldiers ready to fill in  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor London armed police    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Ministry of Defence is offering    
OL,6, soldiers to support armed police in    
OL,7, London after dozens of Met officers    
OL,8, stood down from firearms duties.       
OL,10,FMore than 100 officers have turned in  
OL,11,Fpermits allowing them to carry weapons,
OL,12,Fa source told the BBC. There are more  
OL,13,Fthan 2,500 armed officers in the Met.  
OL,15,FPolice said the action was being taken 
OL,16,Fafter an officer was charged with the  
OL,17,Fmurder of unarmed Chris Kaba, 24.      
OL,19,FMet chief Sir Mark Rowley welcomed a   
OL,20,FHome Office review into armed policing.
